comments.body:
@Luap99, it has not yet been decided to backport this.   I was concerned that it might not be easily doable, so that's why I asked @Honny1 to give it a go in this repo as a Draft.  If we do move forward with this, then yes, we will need to do this backport to at least the other RHEL related repos after v4.9.  We are still talking with the customer and customer support to size the need of this request.

I, too, am concerned about backporting a new feature like this several hops backwards.  More testing is indeed required.

@robbmanes FYI.
